title: Fox BMX presents | Fox BMX in ATX
description:
The Fox Europe BMX team flew overseas to Austin, a week before Texas Toast to enjoy the sunshine, concrete parks, street, and of course to do what Brits are meant to do when they visit Texas… shoot guns! Matt Priest, Greg Illingworth, Lima Eltham, & Leo Forte compliment each others riding and this video is packed with their unique, smooth and stylish riding. You can tell these dudes had a good time and killed it for the lens of Richard “Veesh” Krumm.

Music:
The Foxery 
"Oh, the places you'll go"

Eros and Eschaton 
"Heaven Inside"

Be sure to check our We Live blog for more.
http://www.foxhead.com/welive
